This is a clean-room implementation written from the published LZ4 format
specifications. No third-party source code was copied. Attributions to prior
art and the underlying format/algorithm:

- LZ4 block & frame formats — Copyright (c) Yann Collet. The reference LZ4
  implementation and format documentation are licensed under BSD 2-Clause.
  Format specs:
    https://github.com/lz4/lz4/blob/dev/doc/lz4_Block_format.md
    https://github.com/lz4/lz4/blob/dev/doc/lz4_Frame_format.md

- xxHash (xxHash32), used for the LZ4 frame descriptor checksum —
  Copyright (c) Yann Collet, BSD 2-Clause.
    https://github.com/Cyan4973/xxHash

- lz4js (https://github.com/Benzinga/lz4js), ISC-licensed, acknowledged as
  prior art / inspiration. No code from lz4js was copied into this project.
